body_html:
I just did a fresh install of python 3.6.3 and tensorflow, and the issue is still present. For example:

(python-3.6.3-ve) ___$ python -V
Python 3.6.3
(python-3.6.3-ve) ___$ python -c 'import tensorflow as tf; print(tf.version)'
/home/james/.pyenv/versions/3.6.3/lib/python3.6/importlib/_bootstrap.py:219: RuntimeWarning: compiletime version 3.5 of module 'tensorflow.python.framework.fast_tensor_util' does not match runtime version 3.6
return f(*args, **kwds)
1.4.1

Now, running python3 rnn_tc.py gives the error as above.

Please re-open this issue.
